DOC.brief_summary: The objective of this study is to evaluate tears between habitual contact lens wearers and non contact lens wearers using a Schirmer Strip for tear collection.
DOC.brief_title: Tear Evaluation Between Habitual Contact Lens Wearers and Non Contact Lens Wearers
DOC.criteria: Have no allergic conjunctivitis. Not be using any topical ocular medications. Considered by the Investigator to not be a suitable candidate for participation
